== Usage ==
This template is a shorter version of '''{{tl|Vandal}}'''; it excludes the page moves log and block link, but includes a link to the block log.

The username is also an #anchorname, to aid quick reference on a long page.

<includeonly>{{#ifeq:{{SUBPAGENAME}}|sandbox||
